IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. TEST.

DATA DIVISION.
01 NAME PICTURE IS A(10).
01 AGE PICTURE IS 99.
01 CODE PICTURE IS X(5).
01 MONEY PICTURE IS S9(3)V99.
01 OTHER-AGE LIKE AGE.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MOVE "JOHN" TO NAME
MOVE 25 TO AGE
MOVE "A1B2" TO CODE
MOVE 12.50 TO MONEY
MOVE 30 TO OTHER-AGE
DISPLAY NAME
DISPLAY AGE
DISPLAY CODE
DISPLAY MONEY
DISPLAY OTHER-AGE.